*  3+ years of experience in a market-facing software and enterprise solutions product management role 
*  Ability to communicate effectively with engineering teams to accomplish project goals 
*  Capable of managing multiple stakeholders on the best course of action for the product 
*  Excellent oral and written communication and presentation skills 
*  Able to conceptualize, negotiate and sell ideas internally and externally 
