*  Experience in a Regulatory, Compliance, Risk, or Audit environment 
*  Experience with Financial Crime Risk Management (FCRM) solutions (NICE Actimize), including Anti-Money Laundering (AML), Transaction Monitoring, OFAC Sanctions screening, and Know-Your-Customer (KYC) capabilities 
